data.title: [Offer] Macintosh Garden software
data.meta_description: Hi there I received a copy of the entire MacintoshGarden software library. Files are organized per software product/title. About 3,134 titles.
data.text:
Hi there

I received a copy of the entire MacintoshGarden software library. Files are organized per software product/title. About 3,134 titles. Mostly are CD/DVD/Floppy images. I can write a script to organize, pack with 7z, and upload into the Library via FTP. I am not sure if it is worthwhile to do it.
